{
  "video_id": "IfjI0tVUpbc",
  "title": "I love being a police officer, but we need reform | Melvin Russell",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12817.0,
      "end_time": 15468.0,
      "text": "I have been a police officer for a very, very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15492.0,
      "end_time": 20690.0,
      "text": "And you see these notes in my hand because I&#39;m also a black preacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21305.0,
      "end_time": 22988.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23120.0,
      "end_time": 25227.0,
      "text": "And if you know anything about black preachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25251.0,
      "end_time": 28463.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll close, and then we&#39;ll keep going for another 20 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28487.0,
      "end_time": 29523.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29548.0,
      "end_time": 31941.0,
      "text": "So I need this to keep pushing this thing forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31965.0,
      "end_time": 34214.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been a police officer for a very long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34238.0,
      "end_time": 35818.0,
      "text": "and I mean I predated technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35842.0,
      "end_time": 37438.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m talking about before pagers."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37462.0,
      "end_time": 38695.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38719.0,
      "end_time": 40980.0,
      "text": "Laugh if you want to, but I&#39;m telling the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41400.0,
      "end_time": 45705.0,
      "text": "I predate War on Our Fellow Man -- I mean, War on Drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45730.0,
      "end_time": 47212.0,
      "text": "I predate all of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47855.0,
      "end_time": 49900.0,
      "text": "I predate so much"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49330.0,
      "end_time": 50816.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve been through ebbs and flows"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50840.0,
      "end_time": 53207.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve been through good and bad times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53231.0,
      "end_time": 57389.0,
      "text": "and still I absolutely love being a police officer."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58207.0,
      "end_time": 61958.0,
      "text": "I love being a police officer because it&#39;s always been a calling for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61982.0,
      "end_time": 63362.0,
      "text": "and never a job."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64218.0,
      "end_time": 65583.0,
      "text": "And even with that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66538.0,
      "end_time": 70814.0,
      "text": "my personal truth is that law enforcement is in a crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71616.0,
      "end_time": 73130.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an invisible crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73154.0,
      "end_time": 75780.0,
      "text": "and it has been for many, many years."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76787.0,
      "end_time": 78656.0,
      "text": "Even though we in law enforcement say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78680.0,
      "end_time": 82282.0,
      "text": "\"You know what? We can&#39;t arrest our way out of this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83258.0,
      "end_time": 85680.0,
      "text": "We say in law enforcement things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85930.0,
      "end_time": 87609.0,
      "text": "\"Yeah, it&#39;s illegal to profile.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88800.0,
      "end_time": 89166.0,
      "text": "You know what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89190.0,
      "end_time": 92548.0,
      "text": "In law enforcement, we even agree that we have to adopt this thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92572.0,
      "end_time": 94777.0,
      "text": "and become more oriented to community policing."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94801.0,
      "end_time": 97711.0,
      "text": "And yet all the while, still,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97735.0,
      "end_time": 99932.0,
      "text": "we continue in the same vein,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99956.0,
      "end_time": 103916.0,
      "text": "the same vein that contradicts everything that we just admitted."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105131.0,
      "end_time": 107834.0,
      "text": "And so that&#39;s the reason for me, several years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108313.0,
      "end_time": 111408.0,
      "text": "Because I was tired of the racism, I was tired of discrimination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111432.0,
      "end_time": 114250.0,
      "text": "I was tired of the \"-isms\" and the schisms."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114490.0,
      "end_time": 115429.0,
      "text": "I was just so tired."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115904.0,
      "end_time": 118570.0,
      "text": "I was tired of the vicious cycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118810.0,
      "end_time": 121310.0,
      "text": "and I was tired of it even in the beloved agency"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121334.0,
      "end_time": 124247.0,
      "text": "in the department that I still love today."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 124771.0,
      "end_time": 126900.0,
      "text": "And so my wife and I, we sat down"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126924.0,
      "end_time": 129741.0,
      "text": "and we decided and we targeted a date that we would retire."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 130130.0,
      "end_time": 132734.0,
      "text": "We would retire and I would go off into the sunset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132758.0,
      "end_time": 135591.0,
      "text": "maybe do ministry full time, love my wife a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135615.0,
      "end_time": 137256.0,
      "text": "Y&#39;all know what I&#39;m talking about."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137280.0,
      "end_time": 138685.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138709.0,
      "end_time": 140432.0,
      "text": "But we decided that I would retire."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140456.0,
      "end_time": 143635.0,
      "text": "But then there was a higher power than I."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 144492.0,
      "end_time": 147359.0,
      "text": "There was a love for the city"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 147384.0,
      "end_time": 150584.0,
      "text": "that I loved, that I grew up in, that I was educated in --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150609.0,
      "end_time": 154309.0,
      "text": "a city that pulled my heart back into the system."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 154959.0,
      "end_time": 156221.0,
      "text": "So we didn&#39;t retire."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 156916.0,
      "end_time": 158310.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t retire"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158334.0,
      "end_time": 160798.0,
      "text": "and so what happened was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160822.0,
      "end_time": 164500.0,
      "text": "over the next -- I would say, 18 months, 19 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 165500.0,
      "end_time": 168830.0,
      "text": "I had this passion to implement some radical policing."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 169393.0,
      "end_time": 171124.0,
      "text": "And so now, over the next 19 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 171148.0,
      "end_time": 174991.0,
      "text": "I shifted, and I transcended from being a drug sergeant --"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176277.0,
      "end_time": 178113.0,
      "text": "ready to retire as a drug sergeant --"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 178865.0,
      "end_time": 180699.0,
      "text": "and went from level to level to level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 180723.0,
      "end_time": 183152.0,
      "text": "until I find myself as a district commander,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 183176.0,
      "end_time": 186119.0,
      "text": "commander of the worst district in Baltimore city."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186453.0,
      "end_time": 188154.0,
      "text": "We call it the Eastern District,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 188178.0,
      "end_time": 189788.0,
      "text": "the most violent district,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 189812.0,
      "end_time": 191519.0,
      "text": "the most impoverished district --"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 191543.0,
      "end_time": 195145.0,
      "text": "46 percent unemployment in that district."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 196180.0,
      "end_time": 198238.0,
      "text": "National rating at that time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198262.0,
      "end_time": 201234.0,
      "text": "national rating, the AIDS and the tuberculosis [rating],"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 201258.0,
      "end_time": 203659.0,
      "text": "was always on the top 10 list"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 203683.0,
      "end_time": 206706.0,
      "text": "for zip codes for cities across the nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 206730.0,
      "end_time": 208469.0,
      "text": "or just zip codes across the nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 208493.0,
      "end_time": 211111.0,
      "text": "The top 10 -- I didn&#39;t say state, I didn&#39;t say city --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 211135.0,
      "end_time": 212475.0,
      "text": "that little neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 213911.0,
      "end_time": 216714.0,
      "text": "And I said, you know what? We gotta do something different."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 216738.0,
      "end_time": 219398.0,
      "text": "We gotta do something different. We gotta think radical."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 219422.0,
      "end_time": 221159.0,
      "text": "We gotta think outside the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 221730.0,
      "end_time": 224411.0,
      "text": "And so in order to bring change that I desperately wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 224436.0,
      "end_time": 226143.0,
      "text": "and I desperately felt in my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 226167.0,
      "end_time": 228456.0,
      "text": "I had to start listening to that inner spirit."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 228480.0,
      "end_time": 230912.0,
      "text": "I had to start listening to that man on the inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 230937.0,
      "end_time": 234400.0,
      "text": "that went against everything that I had been trained to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 234772.0,
      "end_time": 236166.0,
      "text": "But we still did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 236190.0,
      "end_time": 238887.0,
      "text": "We still did it because we listened to that inner spirit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 238911.0,
      "end_time": 240172.0,
      "text": "because I realized this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 240196.0,
      "end_time": 244245.0,
      "text": "if I was to see real police reform"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 244269.0,
      "end_time": 247898.0,
      "text": "in the communities that I had authority over for public safety,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 248690.0,
      "end_time": 250972.0,
      "text": "we had to change our stinkin&#39; thinkin&#39;."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 252728.0,
      "end_time": 253881.0,
      "text": "We had to change it."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 253905.0,
      "end_time": 256628.0,
      "text": "And so what we did is we started to think holistically"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 256652.0,
      "end_time": 257967.0,
      "text": "and not paramilitarily."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 258538.0,
      "end_time": 259922.0,
      "text": "So we thought differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 260819.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262180.0,
      "text": "And we started to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 262410.0,
      "end_time": 264352.0,
      "text": "that it could never be and never should have been"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 264376.0,
      "end_time": 265885.0,
      "text": "us versus them."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 266910.0,
      "end_time": 269118.0,
      "text": "And so I decided to come to that intersection"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 269142.0,
      "end_time": 272363.0,
      "text": "where I could meet all classes, all races, all creeds, all colors;"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 272387.0,
      "end_time": 274928.0,
      "text": "where I would meet the businesses and the faith-based,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 274952.0,
      "end_time": 276238.0,
      "text": "and the eds, the meds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 276262.0,
      "end_time": 277770.0,
      "text": "and I would meet all the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 277794.0,
      "end_time": 280623.0,
      "text": "that made up the communities that I had authority over."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 281205.0,
      "end_time": 283164.0,
      "text": "So I met them and I began to listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 283189.0,
      "end_time": 284641.0,
      "text": "See, police have a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 284665.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "Off the top, we want to bring things into the community"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 287284.0,
      "end_time": 290252.0,
      "text": "and come up with these extravagant strategies and deployments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 290276.0,
      "end_time": 292451.0,
      "text": "but we never talk to the community about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 292475.0,
      "end_time": 295303.0,
      "text": "And we shove them into the community and say, \"Take that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 295806.0,
      "end_time": 298203.0,
      "text": "But we said we&#39;d get rid of that stinkin&#39; thinkin&#39;,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 298227.0,
      "end_time": 299775.0,
      "text": "so we talked to our communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 299799.0,
      "end_time": 301667.0,
      "text": "We said, \"This is your community table."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 301691.0,
      "end_time": 303953.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll pull up a chair. We want to hear from you."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 303978.0,
      "end_time": 305918.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s going to work in your community?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 305942.0,
      "end_time": 308710.0,
      "text": "And then some great things started to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 308950.0,
      "end_time": 309246.0,
      "text": "See, here&#39;s the thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 309270.0,
      "end_time": 314990.0,
      "text": "I had to figure out a way to shift 130 cops that were under my tutelage"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 315140.0,
      "end_time": 317126.0,
      "text": "from being occupiers of communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 317150.0,
      "end_time": 318339.0,
      "text": "to being partners."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 319355.0,
      "end_time": 321470.0,
      "text": "I had to figure out how to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 321710.0,
      "end_time": 323500.0,
      "text": "Because here&#39;s the crazy thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 323740.0,
      "end_time": 326719.0,
      "text": "in law enforcement, we have evolved into something incredible."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 326743.0,
      "end_time": 328680.0,
      "text": "Listen, we have become great protectors."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 328704.0,
      "end_time": 330132.0,
      "text": "We know how to protect you."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 330909.0,
      "end_time": 334948.0,
      "text": "But we have exercised that arm so much, so very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 334972.0,
      "end_time": 338138.0,
      "text": "If I was a natural police department"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 338162.0,
      "end_time": 340420.0,
      "text": "and I represented a police department,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 340670.0,
      "end_time": 342956.0,
      "text": "you would see this incredible, beautiful, 23-inch arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 342980.0,
      "end_time": 345583.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 345607.0,
      "end_time": 347686.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s pretty, ain&#39;t it? It&#39;s cut up."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 348641.0,
      "end_time": 351568.0,
      "text": "No fat on it. Mmm it look good. It just look good!"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 351592.0,
      "end_time": 353726.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 353750.0,
      "end_time": 355651.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a great arm -- protection!"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 355675.0,
      "end_time": 358778.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s who we are, but we&#39;ve exercised it so much sometimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 359255.0,
      "end_time": 360810.0,
      "text": "that it has led to abuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 362800.0,
      "end_time": 366300.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s led to coldness and callousness and dehumanized us."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 366941.0,
      "end_time": 368920.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve forgotten"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 368117.0,
      "end_time": 369530.0,
      "text": "the mantra across this nation"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 369554.0,
      "end_time": 371623.0,
      "text": "is to protect and serve."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 372680.0,
      "end_time": 374440.0,
      "text": "Y&#39;all don&#39;t know that? Protect and serve."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 374680.0,
      "end_time": 375680.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 375930.0,
      "end_time": 376498.0,
      "text": "So you look at the other arm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 376522.0,
      "end_time": 378657.0,
      "text": "and then you look at it and ... there it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 378681.0,
      "end_time": 379854.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 380267.0,
      "end_time": 382156.0,
      "text": "You know, it&#39;s kinda weak."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 382926.0,
      "end_time": 384163.0,
      "text": "It looks sickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 384972.0,
      "end_time": 386758.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s withering and it&#39;s dying"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 387861.0,
      "end_time": 390503.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;ve invested so much in our protective arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 391302.0,
      "end_time": 394159.0,
      "text": "But we forgot to treat our communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 394183.0,
      "end_time": 395566.0,
      "text": "like they&#39;re our customers;"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398991.0,
      "text": "like they&#39;re our sons and daughters, our brothers and sisters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 399150.0,
      "end_time": 400205.0,
      "text": "our mothers and fathers."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 400600.0,
      "end_time": 402849.0,
      "text": "And so somehow, along the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 402873.0,
      "end_time": 404304.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve gotten out of balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 404958.0,
      "end_time": 407660.0,
      "text": "And because we are a proud profession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 407952.0,
      "end_time": 411930.0,
      "text": "it is very hard for us to look in the mirror and see our mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 411117.0,
      "end_time": 412838.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s even harder to make a change."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 413775.0,
      "end_time": 416647.0,
      "text": "And so, as I try to hurry and get through this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 417204.0,
      "end_time": 418365.0,
      "text": "I need to say this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 418389.0,
      "end_time": 420331.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not just law enforcement, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 420818.0,
      "end_time": 423149.0,
      "text": "Because every one of us makes up a community."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 423674.0,
      "end_time": 425359.0,
      "text": "Everybody makes up a community."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 425678.0,
      "end_time": 427606.0,
      "text": "And as communities -- can I say this? --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 427630.0,
      "end_time": 431200.0,
      "text": "we have put too much responsibility on law enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 432261.0,
      "end_time": 433419.0,
      "text": "Too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 433443.0,
      "end_time": 437686.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 438706.0,
      "end_time": 441353.0,
      "text": "And then we have the audacity and the nerve to get upset"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 441377.0,
      "end_time": 443480.0,
      "text": "with law enforcement when we take action."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 444265.0,
      "end_time": 445679.0,
      "text": "There is no way in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 446615.0,
      "end_time": 450158.0,
      "text": "that we, as a community, should be calling the police"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 450182.0,
      "end_time": 452710.0,
      "text": "for kids playing ball in the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 454710.0,
      "end_time": 456807.0,
      "text": "No way in the world that we should be calling the police"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 456831.0,
      "end_time": 458917.0,
      "text": "because my neighbor&#39;s music is up too loud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 458941.0,
      "end_time": 461695.0,
      "text": "because his dog came over to my yard and did a number two;"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 461719.0,
      "end_time": 464240.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no way we should be calling the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 464264.0,
      "end_time": 466906.0,
      "text": "But we have surrendered so much of our responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 466930.0,
      "end_time": 470640.0,
      "text": "Listen, when I was a little boy coming up in Baltimore --"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 470880.0,
      "end_time": 472225.0,
      "text": "and listen, we played rough in the street --"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 472249.0,
      "end_time": 474660.0,
      "text": "I ain&#39;t never see the police come and break us up."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 476951.0,
      "text": "You know who came? It was the elders."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 476975.0,
      "end_time": 479110.0,
      "text": "It was the parental figures in the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 479440.0,
      "end_time": 482270.0,
      "text": "It was those guardians, it was that village mentality."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 482510.0,
      "end_time": 485106.0,
      "text": "They came and said, \"Stop that!\" and \"Do this.\" and \"Stop that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 485689.0,
      "end_time": 489411.0,
      "text": "We had mentors throughout all of the community."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 489769.0,
      "end_time": 492900.0,
      "text": "So it takes all of us, all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 492620.0,
      "end_time": 493820.0,
      "text": "And when I say community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 493844.0,
      "end_time": 496871.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m talking about everything that makes up a community, even --"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 496895.0,
      "end_time": 499825.0,
      "text": "listen, because I&#39;m a preacher, I&#39;m very hard on the churches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 499850.0,
      "end_time": 502597.0,
      "text": "because I believe the churches too often have become MIA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 502621.0,
      "end_time": 503777.0,
      "text": "missing in action."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 503802.0,
      "end_time": 506370.0,
      "text": "I believe they have shifted over the last 10, 20 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 506394.0,
      "end_time": 507870.0,
      "text": "from being community churches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 507894.0,
      "end_time": 511362.0,
      "text": "where you walk outside your door, round the corner and you&#39;re in church."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 511386.0,
      "end_time": 514246.0,
      "text": "They shifted from that and became commuter churches."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 514270.0,
      "end_time": 518730.0,
      "text": "So you now have churches who have become disconnected by default"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 518754.0,
      "end_time": 521209.0,
      "text": "from the very community where they&#39;re planted."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 522590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524439.0,
      "text": "And they don&#39;t take care of that community."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 525153.0,
      "end_time": 527821.0,
      "text": "I could go on and on, but I really need to wrap this up."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 527845.0,
      "end_time": 530496.0,
      "text": "Community and policing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 530520.0,
      "end_time": 534821.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve all lost that precious gift, and I call it relational equity."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 535498.0,
      "end_time": 537421.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve lost it with one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 537445.0,
      "end_time": 539460.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not somebody else&#39;s fault --"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 539484.0,
      "end_time": 540808.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s all of our fault."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 541371.0,
      "end_time": 543337.0,
      "text": "We all take responsibility in this."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 543361.0,
      "end_time": 546562.0,
      "text": "But I say this: it&#39;s not too late for all of us to build our cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 546586.0,
      "end_time": 548224.0,
      "text": "and nation to make it great again."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 548248.0,
      "end_time": 549407.0,
      "text": "It is never too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 549431.0,
      "end_time": 550747.0,
      "text": "It is never too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 551428.0,
      "end_time": 552829.0,
      "text": "You see, after three years"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 552853.0,
      "end_time": 556910.0,
      "text": "of my four-and-a-half-year commandship in that district,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 556115.0,
      "end_time": 557269.0,
      "text": "three years in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 557293.0,
      "end_time": 559972.0,
      "text": "after putting pastors in the car with my police"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 559996.0,
      "end_time": 562170.0,
      "text": "because I knew this -- it&#39;s a little secret --"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 562195.0,
      "end_time": 563354.0,
      "text": "I knew this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 563378.0,
      "end_time": 566430.0,
      "text": "it was hard to stay a nasty police officer"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 566670.0,
      "end_time": 568168.0,
      "text": "while you&#39;re riding around with a clergy."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 568192.0,
      "end_time": 570374.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 570398.0,
      "end_time": 576195.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 578476.0,
      "end_time": 582500.0,
      "text": "You&#39;d be getting in and out of the car, looking to your right, talking about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 582290.0,
      "end_time": 585564.0,
      "text": "\"Father, forgive me, for I have sinned,\" all day long -- you can&#39;t do it!"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 585589.0,
      "end_time": 587842.0,
      "text": "So we came up with some incredible initiatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 587866.0,
      "end_time": 591361.0,
      "text": "engagements for our community and police to build that trust back."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 591385.0,
      "end_time": 592944.0,
      "text": "We began to deal with our youth"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 592968.0,
      "end_time": 596146.0,
      "text": "and with those who we consider are on the wrong side of the fence."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 596170.0,
      "end_time": 597902.0,
      "text": "We knew we had an economic problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 597927.0,
      "end_time": 599419.0,
      "text": "so we began to create jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 599443.0,
      "end_time": 601491.0,
      "text": "We knew there was sickness in our community"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 601515.0,
      "end_time": 604900.0,
      "text": "and they didn&#39;t have access to proper medical care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 604330.0,
      "end_time": 605192.0,
      "text": "so we&#39;d partner up."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 605216.0,
      "end_time": 607289.0,
      "text": "We got to that intersection and partnered up"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 607313.0,
      "end_time": 609400.0,
      "text": "with anybody that wanted to partner with us"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 609424.0,
      "end_time": 611591.0,
      "text": "and talked about what we needed holistically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 611615.0,
      "end_time": 613128.0,
      "text": "never thinking about the crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 613152.0,
      "end_time": 614847.0,
      "text": "Because at the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 614871.0,
      "end_time": 616934.0,
      "text": "if we took care of the needs of the people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 616958.0,
      "end_time": 618521.0,
      "text": "if we got to the root cause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 619251.0,
      "end_time": 621438.0,
      "text": "the crime would take care of itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 622599.0,
      "end_time": 624650.0,
      "text": "It would take care of itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 624890.0,
      "end_time": 628744.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 629897.0,
      "end_time": 633979.0,
      "text": "And so, after three years of a four-and-a-half-year stint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 634665.0,
      "end_time": 636341.0,
      "text": "we looked back and we looked over"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 636365.0,
      "end_time": 639730.0,
      "text": "and found out that we were at a 40-year historical low:"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 639754.0,
      "end_time": 642635.0,
      "text": "our crime numbers, our homicides --"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 642659.0,
      "end_time": 645116.0,
      "text": "everything had dropped down, back to the 1970s."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 645140.0,
      "end_time": 646556.0,
      "text": "And it might go back further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 646580.0,
      "end_time": 649497.0,
      "text": "but the problem is, we only started keeping data since 1970."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 649521.0,
      "end_time": 652617.0,
      "text": "Forty-year crime low, so much so, I had other commanders call me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 652641.0,
      "end_time": 654580.0,
      "text": "\"Hey Mel, whatcha doin&#39;, man?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 654820.0,
      "end_time": 656186.0,
      "text": "Whatcha doin&#39;? We gotta get some of that!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 656210.0,
      "end_time": 657625.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 657649.0,
      "end_time": 659308.0,
      "text": "And so we gave them some of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 660968.0,
      "end_time": 662420.0,
      "text": "And in a short period of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 662444.0,
      "end_time": 664721.0,
      "text": "the city went to a 30-year crime low."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 665181.0,
      "end_time": 667830.0,
      "text": "For the first time in 30 years, we fell, Baltimore city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 667854.0,
      "end_time": 670218.0,
      "text": "to under 200 homicides -- 197 to be exact."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 670242.0,
      "end_time": 671401.0,
      "text": "And we celebrated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 671425.0,
      "end_time": 675108.0,
      "text": "because we had learned to become great servers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 675132.0,
      "end_time": 676868.0,
      "text": "become great servers first."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 676893.0,
      "end_time": 679215.0,
      "text": "But I gotta tell you this: these last few years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 680607.0,
      "end_time": 682227.0,
      "text": "as much as we had learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 682856.0,
      "end_time": 685803.0,
      "text": "to become great proactive police officers"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 685827.0,
      "end_time": 689588.0,
      "text": "and great relational police officers rather than reactive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 689612.0,
      "end_time": 691677.0,
      "text": "these last years have disappointed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 692710.0,
      "end_time": 694520.0,
      "text": "They have broken my heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 694644.0,
      "end_time": 696481.0,
      "text": "The uprising still hurts."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 697584.0,
      "end_time": 699270.0,
      "text": "It still hurts my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 699294.0,
      "end_time": 702276.0,
      "text": "because truly I believe that it should&#39;ve never happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 703140.0,
      "end_time": 704807.0,
      "text": "I believe it should&#39;ve never happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 704831.0,
      "end_time": 707775.0,
      "text": "if we were allowed to continue along the vein that we were in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 707799.0,
      "end_time": 709478.0,
      "text": "servicing our community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 709503.0,
      "end_time": 712439.0,
      "text": "treating them like human beings, treating them with respect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 712463.0,
      "end_time": 714260.0,
      "text": "loving on them first."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 714670.0,
      "end_time": 716829.0,
      "text": "If we continued in that vein,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 716854.0,
      "end_time": 718703.0,
      "text": "it would&#39;ve never happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 718727.0,
      "end_time": 721303.0,
      "text": "But somehow, we went back to business as usual."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 721956.0,
      "end_time": 723450.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m excited again!"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 724164.0,
      "end_time": 727509.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m excited again, because now we have a police commissioner"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 727533.0,
      "end_time": 730974.0,
      "text": "who not only talks about community policing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 731800.0,
      "end_time": 734117.0,
      "text": "but he absolutely understands it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 734142.0,
      "end_time": 736214.0,
      "text": "and more importantly, he embraces it."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 736238.0,
      "end_time": 737957.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m very excited now."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 737981.0,
      "end_time": 740930.0,
      "text": "Listen, I&#39;m excited about Baltimore today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 740954.0,
      "end_time": 745203.0,
      "text": "because we, as many cities, I believe shall rise from the ashes."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 745973.0,
      "end_time": 748862.0,
      "text": "I believe -- I truly believe --"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 748886.0,
      "end_time": 749908.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 749932.0,
      "end_time": 751710.0,
      "text": "that we will be great again."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 752639.0,
      "end_time": 753810.0,
      "text": "I believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 754470.0,
      "end_time": 757541.0,
      "text": "as we continue to wrap arms and continue to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 757565.0,
      "end_time": 758763.0,
      "text": "\"We&#39;re in this together,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 758787.0,
      "end_time": 760630.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s not just an intersection:"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 760654.0,
      "end_time": 764288.0,
      "text": "once we meet, we now gotta get on the same path for the same goals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 764312.0,
      "end_time": 766360.0,
      "text": "and this city will become great again."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 766384.0,
      "end_time": 768345.0,
      "text": "This nation will become great again."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 768369.0,
      "end_time": 770788.0,
      "text": "Because we have the same goal: we all want peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 770812.0,
      "end_time": 772546.0,
      "text": "We all want respect for one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 772570.0,
      "end_time": 773720.0,
      "text": "We all want love."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 773744.0,
      "end_time": 775636.0,
      "text": "And I believe we are back on that road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 775660.0,
      "end_time": 777300.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m so excited about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 777540.0,
      "end_time": 780401.0,
      "text": "So listen, I thank you for giving me a few minutes of your time."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 780426.0,
      "end_time": 781656.0,
      "text": "God bless you all."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 781680.0,
      "end_time": 782680.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 782705.0,
      "end_time": 783856.0,
      "text": "God bless you."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 783880.0,
      "end_time": 786301.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}